ule abel: Usoro nnwale maka njikọta nke usoro enweghị ngwụcha
zuru oke convergence: Ekwuru na usoro enweghị ngwụcha ga-agbakọta nke ọma ma ọ bụrụ na nchikota ụkpụrụ zuru oke nke nchikota ahụ nwere oke.
zuru oke: Uru kacha elu otu ọrụ na-enweta
uru zuru oke: Uru na-adịghị mma nke ọnụ ọgụgụ dị adị n'agbanyeghị akara ya
usoro \u1ecdz\u1ecd: Usoro enweghị ngwụcha nke usoro ya na-agbanwe n'etiti ihe dị mma na nke na-adịghị mma
ule usoro \u1ecdz\u1ecd: Usoro eji gosi na usoro ọzọ nwere okwu na-ebelata uru zuru oke bụ usoro na-agbanwe agbanwe
annulus: Ihe yiri mgbanaka, mpaghara ejiri okirikiri concentric abụọ jikọtara ya
antiderivative: Ọrụ dị iche iche nke usoro ya nhata na ọrụ mbụ
asymptote: Ahịrị nke na anya dị n'etiti mgbanaka na ahịrị na-abịaru nso efu ka otu ma ọ bụ abụọ nke nhazi x ma ọ bụ y na-achọkarị enweghị ngwụcha.
mpaghara n'okpuru mgbanaka: Ngwakọta nke na-anọchite anya mpaghara dị n'etiti curve y=f(x), x-axis, na ahịrị kwụ ọtọ x=a na x=b, ebe a na b bụ oke nke njikọta.
agb\u1ee5 iwu: Mwepụta nke ọrụ ihe mejupụtara bụ ihe nrụpụta nke ọrụ dị n'èzí a na-enyocha n'oge ọrụ ime n'ime oge ọrụ nke ime.
mgbako d\u1ecb iche iche: Nyochaa ọnụego mgbanwe nke ọnụọgụ. A na-eji nha nhata akọwa ọnụọgụ mgbanwe nke ọrụ
mgbanwe nke onwe: Ọnụọgụ a na-emegharị n'otu ọrụ ma ọ bụ nhata, na-anọchi anya ihe kpatara ya na mmekọrịta akpata na mmetụta.
agbanwe agbanwe: Nsonaazụ ma ọ bụ rụpụta ọrụ ma ọ bụ mmekọrịta na-agbanwe dabere na ụkpụrụ nke ọnụọgụ ndị ọzọ
ngalaba: Na-ezo aka na ụkpụrụ niile enwere ike iji dị ka ntinye na ọrụ
oke: Echiche nke na-akọwa ihe mmepụta uru ọrụ na-abịaru nso ka ntinye na-abịaru nso na uru ụfọdụ
usoro: Echiche nke na-atụ ọnụego mgbanwe ozugbo ma ọ bụ mkpọda ahịrị tangent n'otu oge na ọrụ.
mkpok\u1ecdta mkpok\u1ecdta: Mgbatị mgbako nke gụnyere ịchọta ihe mgbochi nke ọrụ nke enyere usoro ya
ah\u1ecbr\u1ecb integral: Ngwakọta nke ọrụ n'akụkụ ahịrị nke eriri
n'elu integral: Nchịkọta nke integrals dị iche iche na ntinye n'elu elu
multivariable mgbako: Mgbatị mgbako n'otu mgbanwe gaa na mgbako nwere ọrụ nke ọtụtụ mgbanwe
ubi vector: Ebe dị na mbara igwe nwere oke na ntụzịaka
mgbako vector: Mgbatị mgbako mgbako nke na-ekwu maka ọdịiche na njikọta nke ubi vector na oghere Euclidean nwere akụkụ atọ.
ikike vector: Mpaghara vector nke na-ebute ubi solenoidal site na onye na-ahụ maka curl
